This article provides a compilation of statements made by various individuals praising Judge Sonia Sotomayor's qualifications for the Supreme Court. The statements include praise for her intelligence, experience, pragmatism, fairness, and non-ideological approach to the law. Some notable individuals who praised her include fellow Second Circuit Judge Guido Calabresi, former Chief Judge of the Second Circuit Court of Appeals Jon Newman, Senator Olympia Snowe, Senator Joe Lieberman, and Harvard Law Professor Charles Ogletree. The article also highlights Sotomayor's experience in business law and her ability to ask penetrating but fair questions. Overall, these statements paint a positive picture of Sotomayor's qualifications for the Supreme Court.